* Complete the next 3 segments in any order.
}}
[[File:Chest location for making history quest.png|frame|Chest location]]

===Erin the silver merchant===
{{Checklist|
* Talk to the [[Silver merchant]] in the East Ardougne market. {{Chat option|3Ask about the outpost.}}
* Find the chest buried north of castle wars.
* Open the chest with the enchanted key to get a journal.
}}
===Droalak the Ghost===
{{Checklist|
* Talk to [[Droalak]] outside the Port Phasmatys general store.
* In the building north-east of the general store, give [[Melina]] a strung sapphire amulet.
* Talk to Droalak to receive a scroll.
}}
===Dron the Warrior===
{{Checklist|
* Go to Rellekka and talk to [[Blanin]] east of the longhall. 
* Talk to [[Dron]] north of the longhall. {{Chat option|3I'm after important answers.|2Why, you're the famous warrior Dron!}} Answers:
** Quick answers: {{Chat option|2An iron mace|1Breakfast|2Lunch|1Bunnies|2Red|236|18|3Fifth and Fourth|3North East side of town|1Blanin|1Fluffy|112, but what does that have to do with anything?}}
** He wields an '''iron mace''' in battle. {{Chat option|2An iron mace}}
** He eats '''rats''' for '''breakfast'''. {{Chat option|1Breakfast}}
** He eats '''kittens''' for '''lunch'''. {{Chat option|2Lunch}}
** He eats '''bunnies''' for '''tea'''. {{Chat option|1Bunnies}}
** His favourite drink is '''red''' spider blood. {{Chat option|2Red}}
** He is '''36 years, 8 months (21 days) old.''' {{Chat option|236|18}}
** He studies the '''Fifth''' and '''Fourth''' ages. {{Chat option|3Fifth and Fourth}}
** His house is on the '''northeast side''' of town. {{Chat option|3North East side of town}}
** His brother's name is '''Blanin'''. {{Chat option|1Blanin}}
** His pet cat is named '''Fluffy'''. {{Chat option|1Fluffy}}
** 5 and 7 is '''12''' {{Chat option|112, but what does that have to do with anything?}}
}}
===Reporting back===
{{Checklist|
* Talk to Jorral, back at the outpost, with the scroll and journal.
* Talk to [[King Lathas]], located on the second floor of the palace next to the east/west wall splitting Ardougne.
* Talk to Jorral, back at the outpost.
}}
