==Details==
{{Quest details
|description = [[Prince Ali]] of [[Al Kharid]] has been kidnapped by the scheming [[Lady Keli]]. You are hired to stage a rescue mission.
|start = Speak to [[Hassan]] in the palace at [[Al Kharid]].
|difficulty = Novice
|length = Short (if you start with all items), medium (if you don't)
|requirements = Able to get past aggressive [[combat level]] 26 [[Jail guard]]s.
|items = *[[Redberries]]
*[[Soft clay]] 
*3 [[balls of wool]]
*[[Pot of flour]]
*2 [[onion]]s or 1 [[yellow dye]]
*[[Ashes]]
*A [[bucket of water]]
*1 [[bronze bar]]
*[[Pink skirt]]
*3 [[beer]]s
*[[Rope]] or 18 coins
*At least 50 coins
'''Recommended:'''
|recommended = *[[Amulet of glory]], or [[necklace of passage]] and [[ring of dueling]] for quick travel
*A teleport to [[Varrock]]
}}

==Walkthrough==
===Getting started===
{{Checklist|
*Begin the quest by talking to [[Hassan]], who is in the southern room of the ground floor of [[Al Kharid palace]]. {{Chat option|1Can I help you? You must need some help here in the desert.}}
*Talk to [[Osman]] just north of the palace. {{Chat option|1What is the first thing I must do?|2What is the second thing you need?|3Okay, I better find some things.}}
*Talk to [[Leela]] east of [[Draynor Village]], north of the jail. {{Chat option|1I must make a disguise. What do you suggest?|1I need to get the key made.|2What can I do with the guards?|3I will go and get the rest of the escape equipment.}}
}}

===Obtaining a disguise===
{{Checklist|
*Go to [[Ned]]'s house (just west of Leela) and obtain the [[wig]] from him. {{Chat option|1Ned, could you make other things from wool?|2How about some sort of wig?|1I have that now. Please, make me a wig.}} if [[Dragon Slayer]] is not started or {{Chat option|2Ned, could you make other things from wool?|2How about some sort of wig?|1I have that now. Please, make me a wig.}} if Dragon Slayer is completed or started.
*You may buy a rope from Ned for 15 coins if you do not already have one.
*Go to [[Aggie]]'s house (just west of Ned's house) and use the onion on Aggie to get [[yellow dye]]. (Be careful not to eat the onions!) Right click them and use on Aggie for the dye.
*Talk again to get the [[skin paste]] (ash, pot of flour, bucket of water and redberries). {{Chat option|1Could you think of a way to make skin paste?|1Yes please. Mix me some skin paste.}}
*Go to Varrock clothes shop and purchase a pink skirt
*Use the yellow dye on the wig and retrieve the [[soft clay]].
}}

===Obtaining a key===
{{Checklist|
*Go to the jailhouse east of Draynor Village (big red exclamation mark east of Draynor bank).
*Talk to [[Lady Keli]]. {{Chat option|1Heard of you? You are famous in Gielinor!|2What is your latest plan there?|3Can you be sure they will not try to get him out?|1Could I see the key please?|1Could I touch the key for a moment please?}}
*Return to Osman outside Al Kharid palace to duplicate the key. {{Chat option|1Thank you. I will try to find the other items.}}
*Return to Leela and get the key from her.
}}

===Breaking out===
{{Checklist|
*Go to the jailhouse.
*Talk to [[Joe (jail)|Joe]] and keep offering drinks to him. {{Chat option|1I have some beer here, fancy one?}}
*Use the rope on Lady Keli.
*Use the key on the cell door.
*Talk to [[Prince Ali]]. Use the wig and skin paste on him.
*Report back to Hassan.
}}

