*Talk to [[Aubury]] south of [[Varrock East Bank|Varrock's east bank]] in the [[Varrock rune shop]]. {{Chat option|3}}
*Talk to [[Aubury]] again.
*Take the [[Notes (Rune Mysteries)|notes]] back to [[Wizard Sedridor]].
