The Corsair Curse/Quick guide:
{{Quick Guide}}
{{Infobox Quest
|name = The Corsair Curse
|image = [[File:The Corsair Curse.png|200px]]
|number = 135
|members = No
|release = [[7 December]] [[2017]]
|update = The Corsair Curse and Wilderness Chaos Altar
|series = None
|difficulty = Novice
|developer = Mod Ash
}}
{{ToC}}
{{clear}}
==Details==
{{Quest details
|start = Speak to [[Captain Tock]] at the crossroads north of [[Port Sarim]].
|difficulty = 1
|description = From the newly revealed town of Corsair Cove, deep in the south of Feldip Hills, the captain of the Corsairs has sailed to Port Sarim seeking help. His crew is sick, and he suspects that a curse has been laid upon them.

If you can unravel the fearful and conflicting tales of ogre relics, vengeful mermaids and demonic possession, maybe you can help his ailing crew overcome The Corsair Curse.
|length = Medium
|requirements =
|items =*[[Spade]] (obtainable during quest)
*[[Tinderbox]] (obtainable during quest)
|kills = [[Ithoi the Navigator]] (level 35)
|recommended = '''Recommended:'''
*A [[stamina potion]] to traverse the Cove quicker
}}
==Walkthrough==
===The cursed crew===
[[File:The Corsair Curse quest map.png|thumb|250px]]
{{Checklist|
*Speak to [[Captain Tock]] just south of the entrance to [[Falador farm]]. {{Chat option|2What kind of help do you need?|1Sure, I'll try to help with your curse.}}
*Speak to [[Captain Tock]] on the docks just west of [[Rimmington]]. {{Chat option|1Okay, I'm ready to go to Corsair Cove.}}
*Speak to either [[Arsen the Thief]], [[Cabin Boy Colin]], or [[Gnocci the Cook]], upstairs on the buildings directly west of the platform. {{Chat option|1I hear you've been cursed.}}
*Speak to [[Ithoi the Navigator]], who is found upstairs in the building on the southernmost part of the beach, west and slightly south of the platform. {{Chat option|1I hear you've been cursed.}}
*You can do the next section in any order.
}}

===Arsen's, Colin's and Gnocci's "curse"===
{{Checklist|
*Speak to [[Arsen the Thief]]. {{Chat option|1I hear you've been cursed.}}
*Speak to [[Cabin Boy Colin]]. {{Chat option|1I hear you've been cursed.}}
*Speak to [[Gnocci the Cook]] (upstairs in the building just northwest). {{Chat option|1I hear you've been cursed.}}
**Grab the tinderbox next to him if you don't have one.
**Grab the spade found directly south of his hut (right by tree near water) if you don't have one.
*Speak to Captain Tock (cross gangplank south) to receive the [[Ogre artefact (The Corsair Curse)|ogre artefact]]. {{Chat option|1Arsen says he gave you a sacred ogre relic.}}
*Speak to [[Ithoi the Navigator]].
*Use the telescope in [[Ithoi the Navigator]]'s hut.
*Dig by the lump of sand next to the tree where Gnocci the Cook fished in the cutscene.
**Three steps east of the tropical tree found west of the fishing spot.
*Enter the dungeon to the north and slightly east and speak to [[Chief Tess]]. {{Chat option|1I've come to return what Arsen stole.}}
*Return and speak to Arsen the Thief, Cabin Boy Colin, and Gnocci the Cook.
}}

===Traitor in the midst===
{{Checklist|
*Speak to Captain Tock. {{Chat option|1I've ruled out all the Corsairs' theories...|1So what do I do now?}}
*Speak to Gnocci the Cook. {{Chat option|1I hear it happened straight after dinner.}}
*Speak to [[Arsen the Thief]]. {{Chat option|1I hear Ithoi cooked the meal you ate that night.|1What is the mission Francois is doing?}}
*Speak to Colin the Cabin Boy. {{Chat option|1I hear the Captain's thinking of firing Ithoi.}}
*Speak to [[Ithoi the Navigator]]. {{Chat option|1I hear you cooked the meal they ate before getting sick.|1Maybe because the Captain's thinking of firing you.}}
*Speak to Ithoi the Navigator again.{{Chat option|1I know you've faked the curse.|1I bet I can prove you're well enough to get up.}}
*Use your [[tinderbox]] on the driftwood under his hut.
*Speak to Captain Tock. {{Chat option|1I've seen Ithoi running around. He's not sick at all.|3I'll be back.}}
*Head west again and kill Ithoi the Navigator (level 35).
**Use [[protect from magic]] to take no damage.
*Speak to Captain Tock. {{Chat option|1I've killed Ithoi for poisoning your crew.}}
}}

'''Congratulations, quest complete!'''

==Rewards==
{{Quest rewards
|name = The Corsair Curse
|image = [[File:The Corsair Curse reward scroll.png|center]]
|qp = 2
|rewards =
*Access to [[Yusuf]]'s bank in the [[Corsair Cove]].
}}

{{The Corsair Curse}}

